## 3dxdisp
https://github.com/jtsiomb/3dxdisp
Copyright (c) Ioannis Tsiombikas
License: GNU General Public License v2
The LCD HID protocol (report IDs 0x0C, 0x0D, 0x12, page/column addressing,
bit order) was reverse-engineered and documented by this project. No source
code was copied; only the protocol knowledge was used to implement
SpacePilotLcd.cs independently in C#.

## Aerion SpaceNav Win32 Driver (LGPL 2.1)
License: GNU Lesser General Public License v2.1
The Win32 HID enumeration and report-reading approach in OpenNDOF.HID
(SetupDi device enumeration, HidD_* attribute queries, ReadFile input loop,
DeviceIoControl feature reports) was informed by this driver.

